                <note rend="inline" type="source">710.G1A/306: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chairman of the American Delegation</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hull</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-12-10T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 10, 1933—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>64. Your 41, December 9, 4 p.m. The President agrees that there is no objection
                    to your offering the resolution convening the Third Pan American Financial
                    Conference.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
